parameters:
The entry of the Hikou Group in the project has
accelerated the urban development in Sakuhai City.
However, there are various strange things about
this business.

It is clear that a large amount of investment,
which is completely inconceivable to be in line
with the cooperation and benefits of the
underworld, is being funneled underground, easily
twenty times more than the publicly disclosed
financial information.

In addition, it seems that a large number of
scientists and researchers are also cooperating in
the production of something underground. The
amount of power supply also far exceeds the amount
distributed to the station, even though it is in
the center of the city.

This urban development project is just a cover.
They are probably making something underground.
What exactly are they making? Why are they using
urban development as a cover...?

\n<\N[3]>It's 20 times the amount of urban development
funds...!? What on earth are they investing such a
huge amount for...?

Activating the apparition device that manifests
specific thoughts by using the subliminal device
that enables observation of the universal
unconscious realm and the beacon that marks
specific thoughts.

In theory, it becomes possible to communicate with
the specified apparition, in other words, the
spirit. However, this device has the potential to
have a significant impact on its surroundings as
it physically interferes with the sea of
unconsciousness.

Furthermore, as for the conditions for the optimal
placement of the device within the vortex of
thoughts, it is suggested that a location in the
heart of the city and its bustling crowds would be
ideal.

On (Month) (Day), the patient's condition
worsened. In addition to motor impairment,
headache, and loss of appetite, memory impairment
has also occurred. The vomiting has not stopped
since morning, and the vital signs are abnormal.

The girl patient, after waking up, seemed to have
lost several days of memory and her emotions
became unstable. It's so pitiful... It seems she
can't even write her own name anymore.

...At the stage when we confirmed pediatric
malignant brain tumor, including medulloblastoma,
the complications had already progressed to stage
IV. Symptoms such as headaches and walking
difficulties were prominent.

With the progression of symptoms, signs of
delirium were confirmed, and soon after, symptoms
of hallucinations and auditory hallucinations
appeared. Treatment was physically challenging and
had a low success rate, so the prognosis was
diagnosed as two months to live.
